## What Is Left for Alpha

• **#3** — Add/remove items from collections: UI from within a collection to add items from saves and to remove items; persist immediately.  
• **#4** — Spot creation UI: CreateSpotView from Profile → My Spots → "+"; required fields per list below.  
• **#5** — My Spots list (functional): Replace placeholder with real list of spots the user owns.  
• **#12** — Other-user profile sections: Public collections, spots owned, events hosted always visible; saved items only for approved followers with locked empty state.  
• **#13** — Follow-request management UI: Profile surface to view pending follow requests and approve/decline each.  
• **Review event creation flow** — Confirm Create Event (Profile → My Events → "+") matches the minimum required fields below, immediate publish, and consistent flow with the rest of the app.

