## Creation — minimum required fields

**Event**
- Title
- Description
- Category (food, drinks, music, art, markets, community)
- Address
- Start time
- End time
- At least one image

**Spot**
- Name
- Description
- Category (same set as events)
- Address
- Image

*(Coordinates are derived from address by the app/backend; users enter address only.)*

